!!! WARNING !!!
Do it only if you installed this distro on your host system, not on the virtualbox!
!!! WARNING !!!

Open up terminal and fun following commands in order to uninstall vbox additional packages

sudo post-clean
sudo pacman -Rns virtualbox-guest-utils virtualbox-guest-dkms --noconfirm 
sudo rm /etc/modules-load.d/virtualbox.conf
